| Host | IP | Role | OS |
|------|-----|------|-----|
| DC-01 (`DOMAINCONTROLLER`) | 192.168.10.10 | Domain Controller, DNS | Windows Server 2022 |
| WS-01 | 192.168.10.20 | Domain-joined workstation | Windows Server 2022 |
