| FS-01 | 192.168.10.30 | File server | Windows Server 2022 |
| Kali | 192.168.10.50 | Attacker | Kali Linux 2026.1 |

- **Isolation:** VirtualBox NAT Network, statically addressed `192.168.10.0/24`. No DHCP server (every host static), all members using the DC as DNS. Fully sandboxed from the host LAN.
- **Domain:** `ArsenalDomain.com`, 30 standard users plus service/admin accounts and standard groups.
- **Seeded weaknesses:** shared default password across accounts, privileged accounts reusing that password, decoy credential files on an over-permissioned file share.

